          { question: "Are tolls included in the fare?", answer: "Yes, A13 tolls (about 16 euros) are included in the fixed fare of 235-290 euros. No supplement except extended stop en route or CDG destination." },
          { question: "Can the taxi pick me up at the Vieux Bassin?", answer: "Yes, pickup as close as possible to the Vieux Bassin, your hotel or any address in Honfleur. The driver contacts you 10 minutes before arrival to arrange the meeting point." }
