          { question: "Is there any direct transport Honfleur-Rouen?", answer: "No, there is no station or direct bus from Honfleur to Rouen. The taxi is the only direct solution, taking 55 minutes versus about 2h30 combining taxi and TER via Le Havre." },
          { question: "Can the taxi drop me at Rouen Cathedral?", answer: "Yes, your driver drops you at the cathedral, Place du Vieux-Marche, Rouen-Rive-Droite station or your hotel, as you prefer." }
